 frequently insulted to Depp, calling him an “old fat man” and belittling him, for example, when she was told that Dior planned to use him in an advertising campaign, Dembrowski said. “She said, ‘Dior, why would Dior want to do business with you? They’re about class and they’re about style and you don’t have style,'” she said. Dembrowski also testified that Heard had a tendency to “exaggerate” her brother’s issues with drugs and alcohol and she had never seen him go on a “bender.